CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, page 20, reads: "Mrs. Elizabeth Barrow was hostess for the Allstone Manufacturing Company who had a miniature cast stone house in their booth."
TitMainTitle: Elizabeth Barrow standing next to miniature model of cast stone house in Allstone Manufacturing Company booth, at the 1956 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair in Syria Mosque
